<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>About on NC Chinese Music Ensemble, NCCME</title><link>https://luofugui.github.io/crescent-ccms.io/about/</link><description>Recent content in About on NC Chinese Music Ensemble, NCCME</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 03 May 2026 12:00:00 -0500</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://luofugui.github.io/crescent-ccms.io/about/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Youth Orchestra</title><link>https://luofugui.github.io/crescent-ccms.io/about/youth-orchestra/</link><pubDate>Sun, 03 May 2026 12:00:00 -0500</pubDate><guid>https://luofugui.github.io/crescent-ccms.io/about/youth-orchestra/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="青少年民乐团"&gt;青少年民乐团&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;北卡民乐团青少年民乐团面向热爱中国民族音乐的青少年成员开放。项目采用会费制，帮助学生在稳定的排练和演出安排中提升合奏能力、舞台经验和对中国音乐文化的理解。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The NCCME Youth Orchestra welcomes young musicians who are interested in Chinese traditional music. The program is membership-based and gives students a steady ensemble environment to grow their musicianship, performance confidence, and cultural connection.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="项目安排"&gt;项目安排&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between mt4"&gt;
 &lt;div class="w-100 w-30-ns mb4 bg-near-white br2 shadow-4 pa4"&gt;
 &lt;h3 class="f4 mt0 mb2"&gt;会费制&lt;/h3&gt;
 &lt;p class="f5 lh-copy black-70 mb0"&gt;Members participate through an annual membership fee.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="w-100 w-30-ns mb4 bg-near-white br2 shadow-4 pa4"&gt;
 &lt;h3 class="f4 mt0 mb2"&gt;2 场演出&lt;/h3&gt;
 &lt;p class="f5 lh-copy black-70 mb0"&gt;At least two performance opportunities each year.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Join Us</title><link>https://luofugui.github.io/crescent-ccms.io/about/join/</link><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 12:00:00 -0500</pubDate><guid>https://luofugui.github.io/crescent-ccms.io/about/join/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Become a part of our community.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Leadership</title><link>https://luofugui.github.io/crescent-ccms.io/about/leadership/</link><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 12:00:00 -0500</pubDate><guid>https://luofugui.github.io/crescent-ccms.io/about/leadership/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Our team leaders and directors.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Orchestra</title><link>https://luofugui.github.io/crescent-ccms.io/about/orchestra/</link><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 12:00:00 -0500</pubDate><guid>https://luofugui.github.io/crescent-ccms.io/about/orchestra/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Learn about our orchestra structure.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>